short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension for DOSI platform that help you analyze and summarize DOSI platform

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Description
----------------------
Profile analytics for DOSI to analyze their items and summarize to show floor price and amount of their DOSI items.


Settings
----------------------
1. Open the extension popup by clicking at extension icon on your browser
2. Click at gear icon on the top right of the extension popup
3. Setting extension options
4. Click Save button at the bottom of the option page
